Qn: Create a Pod manifest that requests 100m CPU and 256Mi memory, and limits CPU to 500m and memory to 512Mi.

Solution:

apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
    name: my-busybox
spec:
    containers:
        - name: busybox
          image: busybox
          command: ["sleep","500"]
          resources:
            requests:
                cpu: "100m"
                memory: "256Mi"
            limits:
                cpu: "500m"
                memory: "512Mi"